    "description": "<strong>Welcome to The Cosmic Realm!</strong><br><br>Enter the world of Warmonium, a turn-based tactical strategy game that offers an engaging experience for fans of strategical war-game genres and fantasy lovers alike. With online team-oriented multiplayer combat and an advanced multilevel pathfinding system, Warmonium draws inspiration from board games of the late 90’s to early 2000’s.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/79887dc40f72b4da32f54e8b4f794899.poster.avif?t=1749037318\" width=616 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/79887dc40f72b4da32f54e8b4f794899.webm?t=1749037318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/79887dc40f72b4da32f54e8b4f794899.mp4?t=1749037318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Be The Master of your Army… </strong></h2><br><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Take command of your army and utilize turn-based combat wisely to reap the rewards of victory on the battlefield.<br><br></li><li>Experience a one of a kind multilevel pathfinding system, allowing for complex, varied hex based environments like never before!<br><br></li><li>Go online to play against other players or hone your skills against AI bots.</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/3234369fe7c5f532b44bbca5b78958bf.poster.avif?t=1749037318\" width=616 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/3234369fe7c5f532b44bbca5b78958bf.webm?t=1749037318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/3234369fe7c5f532b44bbca5b78958bf.mp4?t=1749037318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/fb96f5fb9ea7702b114446eda4d6b5fd.poster.avif?t=1749037318\" width=616 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/fb96f5fb9ea7702b114446eda4d6b5fd.webm?t=1749037318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/fb96f5fb9ea7702b114446eda4d6b5fd.mp4?t=1749037318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Develop your creativity with Warmonium’s unique and ever-evolving map editor!</strong></h2><br><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unleash your inner-creative mind with Warmonium’s unique, and ever-evolving map editor.  <br><br></li><li>Share creations with the world, and create your own endless, challenging, and enticing experience! <br><br></li><li>Experience a seamless blend between creative power and the heat of battle with your own tile maps!</li></ul></i> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/92983ae9607a5e73067e46f0638eb91a.poster.avif?t=1749037318\" width=616 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/92983ae9607a5e73067e46f0638eb91a.webm?t=1749037318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/92983ae9607a5e73067e46f0638eb91a.mp4?t=1749037318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize your Units...</h2></strong> <br><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build your own decks and deploy them as units in battle! <br><br></li><li>Choose unit points wisely and build the best combos for your playstyle.<br><br></li><li>New characters every month!</li></ul></i> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/ac8d48f348f06dc7ee7200a62c9c5312.poster.avif?t=1749037318\" width=616 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/ac8d48f348f06dc7ee7200a62c9c5312.webm?t=1749037318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850490/extras/ac8d48f348f06dc7ee7200a62c9c5312.mp4?t=1749037318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Must Play for Strategical War Fans.</strong></h2> <br><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the Lore-rich world of the Cosmic Realm and Armnivarde!<br><br></li><li>Endless creation, and uninterrupted fun for all ages, Warmonium is an experience for all to enjoy!  <br><br></li><li> Ranked mode and Tournaments coming soon!</li></ul></i>",
